{"tid":2325372,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何超欣明年麻省理工畢業 計劃北上清華深造","createTime":"2020-12-14T13:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T04:36:39.000Z","uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"46b7ce7a1c84e0d9eb231da059325ae807f0cb7b","tid":2325372,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R55jAjf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR55jAjf.png&h=6450acfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賭王何鴻燊四房的子女，自幼都得到最好的栽培，仍然就學的四房孻女何超欣，今年才21歲的她本身就讀美國麻省理工學院（MIT），主修管理和建築，有消息指她在MIT畢業後，明年計劃北上進修，準備入讀北京清華大學蘇世民書院。<br />\n<br />\n自幼品學兼優的超欣，小學就讀傳統名校瑪利曼小學，她的運動細胞都強，小學三年級被選為「最有潛質運動員」。賭王何鴻燊生前非常痛錫超欣，2007年曾公開評論幾房女兒的樣貌，他曾說：「阿三（陳婉珍）就個個女都靚，阿四（梁安琪）細女（何超欣）就靚到不得了！」<br />\n<br />\n超欣本月初與阿嫂奚夢瑤在上海出席時尚活動，姑嫂齊齊索爆打扮現身，超欣身上的性感晚裝，罕有騷胸，十分吸睛，即獲不少網友激讚，不讓超模阿嫂專美。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhesKda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhesKda.png&h=690daa82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tBK8tER.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtBK8tER.png&h=a9cd8ace&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"819ae27c43b19bb9800459b5ffd897d160dad51e","tid":2325372,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201214/ZGG5BJINDRF3ZA34EMEH3TVTYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201214%2FZGG5BJINDRF3ZA34EMEH3TVTYQ%2F&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=aa50073d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201214%2FZGG5BJINDRF3ZA34EMEH3TVTYQ%2F&h=4d8ab878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201214/ZGG5BJINDRF3ZA34EMEH3TVTYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"d78884113f993efa5737f897d52695404f85dd64","tid":2325372,"uid":181549,"like":11,"dislike":1,"sc